com.yantra.yfc.rcp

Interface IYRCComboContentProvider


  • public interface IYRCComboContentProvider
    The content provider for combo box table cell editors. Used when the model for the combo needs to be taken from the user based on conditions used by the user.

    Sample Code: 

     clmBindindingData[columnIndex] = new YRCTblclmBindindingDataBindingData();
 clmBindindingData[columnIndex].setAttributeBinding("ProductClass");
 clmBindindingData[columnIndex].setColumnBinding("Product_Class");
 YRCDynamicComboBindingData oPCComboData = new YRCDynamicComboBindingData();
 oPCComboData.setKey("Combo");
 oPCComboData.setDescriptionBinding("CommonCode;CodeShortDescription");
 oPCComboData.setListBinding("CommonCodeList:CommonCodeList/CommonCode");
 oPCComboData.setCodeBinding("CommonCode");
 oPCComboData.setComboContentProvider(new IYRCComboContentProvider(){
        public Element getModel(Element element, String property) {
                Element model = null;
                //Create and return the model associted with the combo box cell editor.
                return model;
        }
 });

    akumar

      • getModel

        org.w3c.dom.Element getModel(org.w3c.dom.Element element,
                             java.lang.String property)
        Method to get the model, for populating the combo box for a table cell editor.
        Parameters:
        element - The element of the current table item (table row).
        property - The property associated with the selected table column (attribute binding of the table column).
        Returns:
        The model to be set for the dynamic combo cell editor.
        See Also:
        YRCDynamicComboBindingData
